      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> The Elevate 2024 Agenda is LIVE! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/loudspeaker.png?v=12\" title=\":loudspeaker:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":loudspeaker:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>As you may have heard, <a href=\"https://monday.com/elevate/location/london/?utm_medium=organic_social&amp;utm_source=community_forum&amp;utm_campaign=agenda\">Elevate 2024</a> is coming IN PERSON to London &amp; NYC! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Our biggest user-focused conference is all about YOU. Our carefully curated sessions are based on your feedback and designed just for you!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Don’t forget to get your early bird tickets while you can! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clock3.png?v=12\" title=\":clock3:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clock3:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/b/cbb66d31583881183579d48982b62572a2a79fbf.png\" title=\"Facebook Community EBT elevate24.2\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/b/cbb66d31583881183579d48982b62572a2a79fbf_2_690x254.png\" alt=\"Facebook Community EBT elevate24.2\" width=\"690\" height=\"254\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Facebook Community EBT elevate24.2</span><span class=\"informations\">2512×926 70.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
